<br>
Is this true?<br>
Is the mages role in plain raids soley as a caster?<br>
What is different about a plain as opposed to other zones except that they are tougher and have better loot?<br>
<br>
Please advise,  Im almost 46 now and have till March to get ready for a couple of raids in hate and fear.  Id like to know how to approach a leader of a raid that is prone to keep pets out of the event.  If for some reason pets arent a good thing in these plain raids it would be good to know why so I can rest on the issue.  Thanks for any input you may have for me. <br>
<br>
